<br>
Another neat thing is it shows percentages on both health and mana.  Health on anything you target &quot;yay that lion is down to 37% health!&quot;.  That's definitely a raid/group friendly thing.  Knowing exact percentage of health on your targets, plus accurate mana percentage per caster.<br>
<br>
Bazaar code is implemented &lt;alt + R&gt; for your bazaar screen, &lt;alt + A&gt; for all people selling.  Basically, when you do the Alt A, you can look for items being sold based on name, class, race, armor/weapon slot, price, seller.  To sell in the Bazaar, apparently here's where those Trader Satchels come into play, wherein you put whatever you're selling in the satchels for it to be considered &quot;buyable&quot;.<br>
<br>
Alot of neat stuff, still playing with it myself (no, not playing like that!!).<br>
